{"body": "Great catch. That's true, it won't work without ActionView yet. I've pushed commit to make it first class dependency and I think we can merge it.\r\n\r\nHowever I think it'll be easy possible to make ActionMailer work without ActionView to make able sending simple emails, which don't require template rendering (http://guides.rubyonrails.org/action_mailer_basics.html#sending-emails-without-template-rendering), without the need of AV.\r\n\r\nI'll work on this later and send another PR not to hold this one.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/23251034", "created_at": "2013-08-26T08:58:26Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11396#issuecomment-23251034", "updated_at": "2013-08-26T08:58:26Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11396, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/strzalek", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e28434223c9c5d2ee0d7f7b7c887b36a?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F673de96b04fa3adcae1aacda704217ef.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/received_events", "gravatar_id": "e28434223c9c5d2ee0d7f7b7c887b36a", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "strzalek", "type": "User", "id": 11562, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/strzalek/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523c79f6bd354364b90010bc"}, "id": 23251034, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11396"}
